# Build context for web-app/Dockerfile. Keep it tiny: ship only the brain (src/)
# and the web monorepo. Everything else (Electron build incl. the 72MB exe, deps,
# caches, logs, secrets) is excluded.
*
!src/
!web-app/

# Inside the allowed dirs: drop deps/build artifacts (rebuilt in the image),
# secrets, and logs.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/*.log
.git
